      "review_title": "The games good, but could use fixing.",
      "review_description": "For example, the reports you send don’t even get them fully banned, only mic banned. It should have a real ban for players that don’t go by the rules and ruin the fun of the game.\n\nSnapturners that spam it repeatedly.\nSnapturners are also a big issue, they spam the button and makes it less fun and harder to get them. Some people will see that as a plus, but it’ll only make people dislike them since they’re spamming it.\n\nSpeedglitchers.\nIt’s an easy fix to this aswell, this is why we need real bans not just mic bans. It ruins everything fun in the game, everybody starts getting toxic.\n\nReal rule chart.\nSome people play weird, which is not going by the rules set by the players. Making the game toxic, less enjoyable, and just awful to play.\n\nI’m a content creator in this game, and I have to deal with this everyday, it’s annoying. Please see this and fix this.",
